{
  "id": "69e9e4d37ffc8fdf7e8ab241",
  "title": "自然農法",
  "created": 1776936164,
  "updated": 1776936512,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e9e4d37ffc8fdf7e8ab241",
      "text": "自然農法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936164,
      "updated": 1776936164
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e4fb000000000081ab78",
      "text": "[Nature Farming]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936187,
      "updated": 1776936192
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e4fb000000000081ab79",
      "text": "[Natural farming]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936187,
      "updated": 1776936193
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e4fb000000000081ab7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936187,
      "updated": 1776936187
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e4e3000000000081ab6a",
      "text": "[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/自然農法 自然農法]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936164,
      "updated": 1776936170
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e4e5000000000081ab6b",
      "text": " 有機農業の一形態。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936166,
      "updated": 1776936247
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e537000000000081ab7e",
      "text": " 昭和20年代に[岡田茂吉]と[福岡正信]により同名の農法がそれぞれ提唱された。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936247,
      "updated": 1776936252
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e534000000000081ab7d",
      "text": " 自然農や、自然栽培とは別物。 ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936244,
      "updated": 1776936262
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e546000000000081ab7f",
      "text": " 法律(JAS法等)で「自然農法」は定義されていない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936262,
      "updated": 1776936262
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e4fd000000000081ab7b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936189,
      "updated": 1776936189
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e551000000000081ab80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936274,
      "updated": 1776936274
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e4fd000000000081ab7c",
      "text": " 1935年から[世界救世教教祖]の[岡田茂吉]は",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936189,
      "updated": 1776936418
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e5e2000000000081ab87",
      "text": " \t「土壌に不純物を入れず清浄に保てば、土壌本来の性能を十分に発揮し作物が栽培できる」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936418,
      "updated": 1776936424
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e5e8000000000081ab88",
      "text": " \tという考えのもとで、[無農薬]・[無肥料]の栽培を始めた。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936424,
      "updated": 1776936424
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e588000000000081ab83",
      "text": " 1936年から東京都世田谷区上野毛の邸宅にて実験的に作物を作り始め、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936329,
      "updated": 1776936413
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e5dc000000000081ab86",
      "text": " 1942年からは水稲にも取り組んだ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936413,
      "updated": 1776936413
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e58c000000000081ab84",
      "text": " 1950年に「無肥料栽培」から「自然農法」へと改称、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936333,
      "updated": 1776936408
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e5d2000000000081ab85",
      "text": " 1953年に「自然農法普及会」を発足させた。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936402,
      "updated": 1776936402
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e584000000000081ab81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936324,
      "updated": 1776936324
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e584000000000081ab82",
      "text": "想像以上に歴史が長い[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936324,
      "updated": 1776936482
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e626000000000081ab8b",
      "text": "\t自然農法の歴史の意外な長さと、新興宗教の歴史の意外な長さ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936486,
      "updated": 1776936512
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9e61f000000000081ab89",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776936480,
      "updated": 1776936480
    }
  ]
}